MediaWiki::Bot::Plugin::PLUGINNAME
==========================

This is PLUGINNAME, a Perlwikipedia plugin designed to for PURPOSE.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Some of the test scripts included with this distribution of PLUGINAME
require a working Internet connection. If the test phase will not
complete because you do not have access to wiki.xyrael.net, you can
(probably) safely install the module anyway.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

WWW::Mechanize
XML::Simple
HTML::Entities
URI::Escape
Carp
Encode
MediaWiki::API

In addition, you must have MediaWiki::Bot version 1.5.2 or greater for plugin support.

